basicObj, java.lang.Cloneable
public class MomentPoleStress
extends Strain

The MomentPoleStress is a class to compute the diffraction shift from the triaxial stress tensor using the moment pole method of Siegfried Matthies. See Siegfried Matthies comments in Sla33.java.

Since:
JDK1.1
